Package sprouts.impl

Class AbstractVariables<T>

java.lang.Object
sprouts.impl.AbstractVariables<T>
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>, Observable, Vals<T>, Vars<T>
public class AbstractVariables<T> extends Object implements Vars<T>
A base class for Vars implementations.
